<p>Well, how about his claim in &#8220;What Uncle Sam Really Wants&#8221; that &#8220;free trade is fine for economics departments and newpaper editorials, but nobody in the corporate world or the government takes the doctrines seriously&#8221;?</p>

<p>As a reasonably senior member of the Clinton Treasury, I assure you that we took&#8212;and take&#8212;the doctrine of free trade very seriously indeed.</p>

