<p>Congratulations to Oliver, and kudos as well to Aaron for taking Oliver&#8217;s evidence seriously.</p>

<p>Responding to nimc:  PPS/1 was an internal, top-secret document.  Hitler&#8217;s peace propaganda was exactly that:  propaganda for public consumption.  If you look at the Nazi archives, while Hitler was proclaiming himself to be a man of peace in public he was secretly planning for war.  (For a good narrative history, see Shirer&#8217;s &#8220;The Rise and Fall of the Third Reich.&#8221;)</p>

